OL,5,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIn West Sussex, The Kings Head Inn
OL,7,     Fhosts Colin and Oonagh hope to get
OL,8,     Foff to a flyer of a start with a
OL,9,     Fvisit to a World War II aviation
OL,10,     Fmuseum. But one B&Ber has a hot
OL,11,     Fand sweaty night.
OL,12,G1855 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FVisit two is to The Roade House
OL,14,     F(no, not that one) in
OL,15,     FNorthamptonshire, where hosts Paul
OL,16,     Fand Maxine boast a cafe bar, yoga
OL,17,     Fstudio and hair salon.
