OL,5,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FJoanne and Julie host at The
OL,7,     FHalfway House Inn, in Morley, West
OL,8,     FYorkshire. Two B&Bers poo-poo the
OL,9,     Flack of shampoo, while another
OL,10,     Fpair come to blows at the Royal
OL,11,     FArmouries in Leeds.
OL,12,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe B&Bers are off glamping at
OL,14,     FSanath and Amelia's Stamford
OL,15,     FMeadows Glamping site in
OL,16,     FLincolnshire. But for one pair,
OL,17,     Fthe walk to the WC proves a step
OL,18,     Ftoo far.
